data.description: Look No Further!!! This 3BR/2BA Country Home with 18 Acres was Totally Remodeled in 2022! Situated between Brookhaven & Wesson, this secluded gem has 18 Acres mostly wooded & Ready for Hunting Season with Deer & Turkey. The House has been completely remodeled (2022) with all new LVT Flooring, Refinished Original Hardwood Floors, New Master Suite with Huge Walk-In Closet, New Interior/Exterior Paint, Stainless Steel Gas Stove & Dishwasher, New Aerobic Sewer Treatment Plant, New HVAC System and New Light Fixtures. Also Included is a Full Length Covered Front Porch, 30' x 40' Workshop & Storage Shed. (Some of the Pictures are from 2022 & Used By Permission.) Schedule Your Appointment Today - This Gem Won't Last Long!!!
